Type: Package
Package: SummaryTables
Title: Publication-Ready Summary Tables for Jamovi
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nour Edin", "Darwish", , "nouredindarwish@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0009-5527-4539"))
Description: Create presentation-ready summary tables with descriptive
    statistics and group comparisons. Supports continuous and categorical
    variables with flexible summary statistics, statistical testing
    (t-tests, ANOVA, Wilcoxon, Chi-square, Fisher's exact), effect sizes
    (Cohen's d, Hedge's g, SMD), confidence intervals, and p-value
    adjustment. Includes journal-specific formatting for JAMA, The Lancet,
    NEJM, and QJE. Tables can be exported to Word. Built on the
    'gtsummary' package. Also available as a module for 'jamovi' (see
    <https://www.jamovi.org> for more information).
License: GPL (>= 2)
